    <p>Ital­ian firm CoeLux re­pro­duces a nat­u­ral sun­light ef­fect us­ing cut­ting-edge LED tech­nol­ogy and a wafer-thin nano-struc­tured ma­te­rial that gives the im­pres­sion that the sun is shin­ing through its pan­els with a blue sky as the back­drop.</p>
    <p>Re­search has shown that the light pro­duced by CoeLux pan­els, which are mar­keted in Sin­ga­pore by P5 Lu­mi­naire at Henderson In­dus­trial Park, is also ben­e­fi­cial for or­na­men­tal plant growth. Info: $15,000 to $20,000 from www.coelux.com</p>

